run-exp.sh: generates a makefile of all report files necessary
            sh run-exp.sh | Makefile -c - all 
               should work

mk-alt-arffs.sh: generates second style arff files (not bayesian)

weka.sh: starts weka

TextCount.pl: turns markup_report markup_report.orig into arff files of word counts
arff-join.pl: combine arff files into one
arff-mapper.pl: map tags from detailed to the subtags
                
convert-abez-style-to-postgresql-style.pl: convert our markup stuff to a nice csv style?
convert-abez-style-to-second.pl: convert our reports to a nice arff file

csv2tex.pl: make latex out of a csv file
